SUMMARY:Brock Tract Loop in Goodwood must be good!
DESCRIPTION:These Boots Are Made for Hiking\n**Meetup Point: *1401 Brock R
 oad\,* Goodwood\, ON L0C 1A0**\n\nThe Brock Tract trail offers a great opt
 ion for an immersive escape into nature with a well-maintained trail that 
 explores a mix of woodlands and open fields. Located in the Uxbridge Woodl
 ands of Ontario\, this trail is ideal for those looking for a trail that e
 xplores the forests and open fields of this area. Along the way\, you'll f
 ind a variety of wildlife and enjoy views of the surrounding landscape.\nW
 ear weather appropriate gear please\, which means good hiking shoes that w
 ear well in mud\, slush and snow as we are in the in between weather. Hiki
 ng poles would be helpful as well cause it can be slippery at the time of 
 year.\nLots of water and snacks is suggest as this is a 15km loop.\nOnce y
 ou are in you are in!
