UID:event_313749628@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260317T184540Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260418T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260419T170000
SUMMARY:Time to learn New Skills - Trecking Training  - Two Day Hike with 
 Full Gear
DESCRIPTION:These Boots Are Made for Hiking\nMeet up Point: 6700 Salmon La
 ke Road\, Sydenham\, ON K0H 2T0\, Canada\n**Two days...sat and sun**\n**Fe
 e for Trekking Training: $99.**\n\nWe have a secret and an agenda. We want
  you (and all our members) out Treking. At least once. Don't give up your 
 Sunday hikes\, but hey it's time to up your hiking game!\nWhich is why we 
 are offering skills training for future trekkers so they can join in on tr
 ekking adventures outside of Ontario.\nThere is a lot to learn to prepare 
 for a multi day trekk\, and we want you to be prepared. It is not just kno
 wing what equipment to buy\, how much to carry\, tent set up\, it's also f
 ood prep\, attitude\, and emergency skills and so much more!\nSo\, in orde
 r for you to ensure you have a safe and the very BEST trekking experience 
 we are offering a day in Big Salmon Lake.\n**Experienced Boots Trekkers fe
 el free to hop in and show them how it's done!**\nWe will cover in one wee
 kend -\n\n* your weighted pack\n* pack pacing\n* water filtering\n* trail 
 etiquette\n* safety\n* equipment must haves\n* first aid\n* attittude adju
 stment\n* fire starting\n* navigation\n* ...and more\n\nA zoom call will h
 appen **Thurs. March 19** where we share what you need to bring and answer
  your questions. Zoom details are coming.
